WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.300 --> 00:00:01.866
When I was cornered

2
00:00:02.266 --> 00:00:04.633
It was Mr. Su who gave me new hope

3
00:00:05.366 --> 00:00:06.866
Gave me a new family

4
00:00:07.066 --> 00:00:08.233
New Life

5
00:00:09.166 --> 00:00:10.800
Now Master Su is seriously ill

6
00:00:11.600 --> 00:00:12.700
Urgent need of assistance

7
00:00:13.100 --> 00:00:14.866
Only your kidney can save him

8
00:00:16.166 --> 00:00:18.600
So you came to me last night

9
00:00:19.400 --> 00:00:21.233
Not to meet me

10
00:00:22.666 --> 00:00:25.266
I just want to confirm my identity

11
00:00:25.366 --> 00:00:28.500
Then give my other kidney to Su Jinhui as well

12
00:00:28.500 --> 00:00:30.500
Right? Right.

13
00:00:30.866 --> 00:00:32.200
That's it.

14
00:00:33.300 --> 00:00:34.500
You have to understand

15
00:00:35.166 --> 00:00:38.666
If you live, Master Su will die.

16
00:00:38.900 --> 00:00:40.900
Li Huilan will die too

17
00:00:41.533 --> 00:00:44.033
It's not good for everyone that you're alive

18
00:00:45.200 --> 00:00:47.766
I don't mind. It's for your own good.

19
00:00:47.966 --> 00:00:49.833
Don't want to be sad

20
00:00:50.366 --> 00:00:51.833
Hurt me so sad

21
00:00:52.100 --> 00:00:53.866
So I deserve to die

22
00:00:54.866 --> 00:00:57.233
Everyone thinks I deserve to die

23
00:00:57.700 --> 00:01:00.800
Should I have died 15 years ago?

24
00:01:00.966 --> 00:01:02.600
You understand

